{"id": 1544, "genre": 1000, "title": "你认同哪些“社交网络真实自我”定律？", "description": "每天看到的这么多朋友圈，哪些更（不）可信一些？（题图来自：Antti Kalevi）", "record_count": 27612, "comment_count": 47, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170228144119WjTKbLw4MAy2BURc.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-01T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 1980, "title": "你认同哪些“社交网络真实自我”定律？", "content": "你认同哪些“社交网络真实自我”定律？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 172416, "content": "如果同时使用多个平台，真实自我程度是“豆瓣>微博>朋友圈”", "image": "img/option/option/20170228145950z4ePZUWHKG7IqySX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 172417, "content": "负能量往往比正能量走心", "image": "img/option/option/20170228150808XGMF0TfjNKpnhgsr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 172418, "content": "Po出的合照上人越多，配的文字可能越虚伪", "image": "img/option/option/20170228151254ZsVgfn7wFjpByJkc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 172420, "content": "关于工作的内容也基本上不是真心话", "image": "img/option/option/201702281519027GbNh8QkTyse64fI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 172422, "content": "“自黑”永远是捡自己的优点或者不算太差的方面黑", "image": "img/option/option/20170228152234pdbKvc53TkISWZis.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 172426, "content": "有些表达可能在说相反的意思，比如“我不在乎”", "image": "img/option/option/20170228160434UaYjAxcsTwirmoVb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 172428, "content": "三更半夜没什么人在线的时候最容易发一些莫名其妙的真话", "image": "img/option/option/20170228161220Ahca4Wli9pqjELJV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}